de.mnl.osgi.bnd.maven

Class ExtRevision

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mnl.osgi.bnd.maven.ExtRevision

  • public class ExtRevision
extends Object
    A revision with the a reference to the maven repository in which it was found.

    For some incomprehensible reason, Revision has only an invisible constructor. So it cannot be extended.
